<varlistentry id="options.AlignContents">
	<term>AlignContents <emphasis remap='I'>Left,Top,Right,Bottom,HTiled,VTiled,HScaled,VScaled,HCenter,VCenter</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>That will force contents of each Wharf's button to be aligned to either
        side of the button, when FitContents is not used.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="Align#synopsis">Alignment flags</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
